This paper deals with game theory and mechanism design, which are typically categorized under cs.GT (Game Theory and Economics) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses learning behavior, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Finally, the paper deals with revenue optimization, which is a topic in cs.EC (Electronic Commerce).
